{
  "stem": "10699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Vichy government had formed a new-- a, a new kind of army, which was the Milice, which was a kind of SS, you know, it was a German SS.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They worked for the German government under Vichy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The next day my father who was out looking for food, he came back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were waiting for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, you see, they got one after the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, they-- and eventually took us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we were all in the barracks there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From the 17th, we were there-- I write the date here-- till the 26th of May.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it was-- the 17th of May was a beautiful day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had made arrangements for some friends to go to the countryside with our bicycles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was Ascension Day in France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were all looking forward to get away from Saint-Etienne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was the day we were all arrested.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the sad part was, as it was getting so dangerous, my mother had found the week before in a convent in Le Puy, they were going to, to take us in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, it was a matter of days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were now frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was only one thing to do-- is to leave Saint-Etienne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were leaving in a few days' time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the cellar, we had a reserve of food, you know, eggs, and potatoes, and everything, in case we couldn't go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, the situation was now bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were ready to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The sad part, the unfortunate part was that my mother was that day with the wine merchant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were looking for the Hungarian family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was so unlucky and so tragic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my poor mother, you know, she couldn't forgive herself [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that she happened to be there at that very moment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] By then-- by now we were all together in that-- in that-- in that barracks, army barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on the 26th, when they took us, we were now a whole train of Jewish people-- families.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took us to the station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Gestapo [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] chief came over to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he said to me, if it wasn't for your Milice, you wouldn't be on that train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, he was trying to clear his conscience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then he said, don't try to escape, he says.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He said, otherwise, the other members of your family will be shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And hold and behold, when we came back after the war-- after the-- after the camps, this company said, you know, we have some money for you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't know where it comes from.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever it was, you know, 30 pounds, 40 pounds, and something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And that's how, you know-- that's-- that was his-- there, he was going to evade-- if I try to run away, I would be shot.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the other hand, I give you money for your typewriter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How to explain that, I can't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was member of the OSE.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] And he was at the Swiss border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was caught with his wife, who was 24, 23, and two little children-- four years and 18 months, something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were on their way to Switzerland because they went with the-- with the whole of the town to Cognac, to the other side.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were caught there, too, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were now with us in the same transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were hundreds and hundreds of people there, thousands of them there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the conditions were terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we didn't know what was going to happen to us yet, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when-- we stayed-- a few days we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We stayed there in Drancy three, three nights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We leave on the 30th.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we must have stayed from May till the-- from the 18th-- from the-- five days about, yes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We stayed about five days in Drancy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they took us to the-- a whole-- 2,000 people they took to the station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was one case where the lorries that were standing there, the person that was there-- there was a woman there with a girl of about 10 or 12.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she pretended to be mad because she didn't want to go on a-- on, on, on the-- on the-- truck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I can see only by hindsight, but she knew what was happening better than we did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us to the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
